Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Tobacco brands at the 1991 World Baseball Series
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yh58w
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 1 Nov 1991
Why the Federal Trade Commission decided to ban the sight of tobacco brand names on TV after the 1991 World Baseball Series between the Minnesota Twins and the Atlanta Braves.